dataset_id: Atlantic High Latitude Sea Surface Temperature - Multimission
title: Atlantic High Latitude Sea Surface Temperature - Multimission
summary: Calculation of underskin temperature (°C) with multispectral algorithm. The product covers the Atlantic High Latitudes and is delivered twice daily on a 5km polar stereographic grid.
